<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - Mockly" description="Privacy policy for Mockly mock API service">
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
    <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> / Mockly
  </p>

  <h1>Mockly Privacy Policy</h1>
  <h2 style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-top: 0;">Mock API Service for Developers</h2>
  <p style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">Last Updated: December 2025</p>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Mockly is a mock API service that provides developers with mock endpoints, dynamic responses, 
    and debugging utilities for API development and testing.
  </p>

  <h2>Information Collected</h2>
  
  <h3>Operational Logs</h3>
  <p>For service reliability and security, we may log:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Request timestamps</li>
    <li>IP addresses (standard web server logging)</li>
    <li>Requested endpoints</li>
    <li>Error traces (for debugging)</li>
  </ul>

  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <strong>Important:</strong> Logs are for debugging and abuse prevention only. 
    No profiling or personalization occurs.
  </p>

  <h2>Data You Send to Mockly</h2>
  <p>
    Customer data sent via API requests is <strong>processed in memory and not retained</strong> 
    unless explicitly requested with "log mode" for debugging purposes.
  </p>

  <h2>Personal Data</h2>
  <p>
    Mockly does not collect personal identifiable information (PII) unless you explicitly 
    configure it to log request bodies for debugging.
  </p>

  <h2>User Accounts (Future)</h2>
  <p>
    If Mockly supports authentication or user accounts in the future, a separate privacy 
    policy update will be published detailing data collection.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p style="padding: var(--spacing-md); background: var(--color-border); margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;">
    <p><strong>Hosting:</strong> Vercel or Fly.io</p>
    <p><strong>Optional Analytics:</strong> Privacy-respecting analytics (if enabled)</p>
    <p><strong>No tracking or profiling:</strong> We do not share user data with advertisers or data brokers</p>
  </p>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>
    Operational logs are typically retained for up to 30 days for debugging and security purposes. 
    Custom data is not retained unless explicitly stored by the user.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For privacy inquiries, contact us at:<br />
    <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dps.manit@gmail.com">dps.manit@gmail.com</a>
  </p>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p><a href="/privacy">‚Üê Back to Master Privacy Policy</a></p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
